					<em><figcaption>Pamukkale in Denizli province, Turkey</figcaption></em>
				</span>
			</figure>
		</div>
		
		
		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
			<p class="show-text">
				Turkish Angora cat is a breed of domestic cat that has been bred in Turkey for centuries originating from the city of Ankara. It is a silky-long haired white cat that has often two different eye colors. Besides their unique looks, Turkish Angoras are known to be highly intelligent and easy to train, even deaf ones!
			</p>
		</div>
		
		
		
